title: The Daniel Plan in Action Workout System
description:
THE DANIEL PLAN IN ACTION TOTAL FITNESS SYSTEM

The Daniel Plan In Action: Accelerated is a 40-day fitness system with an innovative approach to creating a healthy lifestyle, rooted and framed by five life areas: faith, food, fitness, focus, and friends. Three expert instructors lead the variety of inspiring workouts with a strong backbone of faith and community, complimented with an exclusive soundtrack of Christian music. This eight-session system focuses on an abundance of healthy choices offering you the encouragement and inspiration you need to succeed.

Included with the 8-Workout 40-Day Program:

Quick Start Guide
Workout Calendar
Nutrition Guide
10-day Detox Guide
